| **Config Schema (Zod)** | `/home/aiscend/work/oh-my-opencode/src/config/schema.ts` | TypeScript (Zod) | Runtime validation schemas |
| **User Config** | `~/.opencode.json` | JSON | User-level configuration overrides |
